## File conventions

This project follows the Diecast file conventions. The canonical spec is
[`docs/specs/cast-init-conventions.collab.md`][conventions-spec] in the
[Diecast repo][diecast-repo]:

- **Authorship suffixes:** `.human.md`, `.ai.md`, `.collab.md` (with graduation rule).
- **Date prefixes:** `YYYY-MM-DD-<slug>.md` for top-level plan/design files.
- **`_v2` versioning:** preserves load-bearing prior versions (use sparingly).
- **Flat-vs-folder heuristic** for `<goal_name>` directories.

The spec is the **single source of truth**. Do not duplicate the rules here — keep this
section a pointer so updates to the spec propagate automatically.

[conventions-spec]: https://github.com/sridherj/diecast/blob/main/docs/specs/cast-init-conventions.collab.md
[diecast-repo]: https://github.com/sridherj/diecast

## Where artifacts land

| Agent | Default write path |
|---|---|
| `/cast-refine` | `docs/requirement/<goal>_requirements.human.md` (flat) or `docs/requirement/<goal>/requirements.human.md` (folder) |
| `/cast-goal-decomposer` | `docs/exploration/<goal>/decomposition.ai.md` |
| `/cast-explore` | `docs/exploration/<goal>/` (subdirectory per goal) |
| `/cast-web-researcher` | `docs/exploration/<goal>/research_notes.ai.md` |
| `/cast-code-explorer` | `docs/exploration/<goal>/code_exploration.ai.md` |
| `/cast-playbook-synthesizer` | `docs/exploration/<goal>/playbooks/` |
| `/cast-high-level-planner` | `docs/plan/<date>-<goal>-overview.collab.md` |
| `/cast-detailed-plan` | `docs/plan/<date>-<goal>-<phase>-detail.collab.md` |
| `/cast-update-spec` | `docs/spec/<spec>.collab.md` |
| `/cast-orchestrate` | `docs/execution/<goal>/<phase>/` |
| `/cast-subphase-runner` | `docs/execution/<goal>/<phase>/<subphase>/` |

See the [conventions spec][conventions-spec] for the complete agent table including the
`cast-preso-*` family and `cast-task-suggester`.

