## Customization

- **User-level config:** `~/.cast/config.yaml` — terminal preference, auto-upgrade,
  upgrade snooze, proactive defaults. See
  [`docs/config.md`](https://github.com/sridherj/diecast/blob/main/docs/config.md) in the
  Diecast repo for the canonical schema.
- **Project-local conventions:** edit this file (`CLAUDE.md`) to override conventions for
  this project only. Agents read this file before they read the global spec, so a
  project-local override wins.
